Suspected vulnerabilities:
- PROTOTYPE-POLLUTION

Function code:
```javascript
function deepMerge(obj1, obj2) {{
    Object.keys(obj2).forEach(key => {{
        if (typeof obj2[key] === 'object') {{
            obj1[key] = deepMerge(obj1[key] || {}, obj2[key]);
        }} else {{
            obj1[key] = obj2[key];
        }}
    }});
    return obj1;
}}
```

